## Critical Commands Reference

| Command / Action | Purpose |
|------------------|---------|
| `parse-prd --input FILE` | Generate tasks from PRD |
| `analyze-complexity --output json` | Create complexity report |
| `complexity-report` | View complexity summary |
| `expand --id=X --num=N` | Break task into N subtasks |
| `next` | Get next executable task |
| `list` | Show all tasks (top-level only) |
| `show --id=X` | Show task details |
| `complete --id=X` | Mark **parent** task done (does not update subtasks) |
| Update `tasks.json` subtasks | After completing a parent, set `subtasks[].status` to `"done"` or leave `"pending"` so progress is accurate |
| Create/update task summary doc | After completing a task, write `.taskmaster/docs/task-summaries/task-<id>.md` with what was done (parent + subtasks) |
| `python .taskmaster/scripts/json_to_csv.py` | Regenerate `tasks.csv` from `tasks.json` (run whenever tasks.json is updated) |
| `generate` | Create task files |

