## Workflow Summary

```
1. Configure providers → config.json
2. Write/refine PRD → prd.txt
3. Parse PRD → tasks.json
4. Analyze complexity → complexity report
5. Iterate (expand or modify PRD) until 90% under threshold
6. Execute tasks in order (next → implement → complete → repeat)
7. After complete: if task has subtasks, update subtasks[].status in tasks.json (done vs pending) so progress is accurate
8. Create or update task summary doc: .taskmaster/docs/task-summaries/task-<id>.md (what was done for parent + subtasks)
9. Whenever tasks.json is updated: regenerate tasks.csv with python .taskmaster/scripts/json_to_csv.py
```
